headline.main: I.L.O. ASKED TO FIX POST-WAR AIMS; Reconstruction Program Is Presented to Conference by American Delegation

lead_paragraph: A program of post-war world reconstruction was presented yesterday by the American delegation to the conference of the International Labor Organization at its session at Columbia University.
